title: INSIGHT: Putin walks through history
text:
INSIGHT: Putin walks through history 7:34pm IST - 00:40 
Vladimir Putin looks set to win a fourth term as Russian president on Sunday. And the ensuring inauguration process at least will be all too familiar.
